Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.36,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利绘 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.40,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}早上好 小夜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.31,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}杏里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.66,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.83,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你怎么又出那么多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.95,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为人家不甘心的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.87,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有人家是骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.25,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这太狡猾了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.00,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这就是我们以前经历的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.13,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我就是因为没人送 所以老是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.51,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃的家里啊 确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:00.64,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为了告别那样惨淡的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.38,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}到了16岁我马上就要去考驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.61,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一定要等我啊 我的小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.27,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}出现了 祖玛爱车宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.36,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小夜前辈 不是祖玛 是小祖才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.82,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我把商品目录拿来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.53,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.24,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}杏里前辈 春乃前辈你们也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.70,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很可爱对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.95,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}把这个拿去凉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.34,Default2,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是问卷调查而已 不用想太多的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:39.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就算那样说...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.23,Default2,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}还有三分钟上交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.05,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦？有新人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:05.51,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}快要到旅游旺季了 所以人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.01,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fscx77.5\fscy76.25\pos(310,442)}小祖状态不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.01,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这次是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.51,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.68,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是个好人就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.64,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.27,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就像电影中的管家那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.40,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}管家啊...
