Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.20,Default2,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃大小姐 请问您是先用餐还是先泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:30.00,Default2,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}打扫洗衣服和客房的准备 以及打扫鸡舍都已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:35.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(290,36)}（难以想像）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.30,Default2,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}作业和应试考题都请交给在下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.70,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦 白日梦结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.03,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.74,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}遇见出色的管家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.70,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.66,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不过真的很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.25,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}反正很快就会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.50,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}总是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:59.47,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}最后都说什么[在自然中找回自我了]之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.14,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.72,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哎 去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.01,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}先去看看是个怎样的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哎 去我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.89,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那我先给哥哥发个邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.27,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.02,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.00,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}风...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.09,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好帅！
