Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.40,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.20,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来 请品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.70,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.75,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.83,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}还真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.12,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}混杂在一起的危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.71,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}比看起来还危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.96,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}加油的话 还是能咽下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.42,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.88,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}接下来是第二弹 准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.35,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.85,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}蛋浇饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.23,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要这样混合起来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:19.06,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我搅 我搅 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.57,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦 超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:25.95,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.16,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}日本的清幽意境真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.75,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}超感动的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.33,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这还不至于吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.46,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃真神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.00,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}该算是误会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.24,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘛 虽然应该不是坏人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:13.16,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但我不认为她适合呆在这小村庄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.75,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.63,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}HI 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.55,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.67,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.00,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你为什么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.51,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}从汐崎妈妈那里听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.97,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.77,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这真耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.23,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\alpha&H33&}这真耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.98,Default2,Cynthia,0208,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\alpha&H77&}...眼!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.57,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哇 超级棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.74,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这里明明是唯一能独处的地点的说...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.41,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}妈妈也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.03,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.62,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这茶和这里美丽的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.56,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}蛋浇饭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.52,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天就让我见识到3个从没见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.88,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没有啦 并不是我有多厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:13.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}话说 去过很多国家的辛西娅才厉害的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.67,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃也要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.18,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不用了 那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.04,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:18.98,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能就是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.69,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能就是不可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:32.49,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我是从什么时候 觉得是这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.24,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:35.91,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.16,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再来一杯 我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.79,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 再来一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.07,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.99,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就这样一直奔跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.22,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}根本就看不见人家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.68,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好像美国的中西部就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.01,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 好像很爽的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.57,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不过 中途终于到了晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.98,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}于是 于是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.02,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我打算就在那野营
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.73,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}然后听见狼的嚎叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.40,Default2,Rie+Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:11.07,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.70,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你居然开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:16.53,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骑摩托和狼赛跑很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.28,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.96,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}外面广阔的世界...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}结果总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.68,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.18,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}反正都是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:47.52,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}然后在河边 离小岛有一点距离的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:52.65,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}木筏开始下沉 只有全力起跳才能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.45,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就算觉得不行 也只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.51,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}HI 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:05.62,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.38,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.83,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}平时的白日梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.46,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.80,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.22,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也想像辛西娅小姐那样去国外飞奔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.51,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.97,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和小祖一起 哪里都想去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.90,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这份感觉是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:32.48,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为知道想做的事不可能全部都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:38.07,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我能做到的事情 也一定不会是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:42.16,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就算离开这里 一定也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:46.46,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}咦？难道我在羡慕她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.50,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}感觉自己好渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.98,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一大早开始脑袋就昏昏沉沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:08.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}可能是因为昨天做的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.11,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小夜获得了诺贝尔文学奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.36,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小杏成为了了不起的作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:17.07,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利绘仔驾着巨大的摩托车飞翔于天际
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:22.03,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}而我 却在给大家送鸡蛋 真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:28.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为辛西娅的到来每天都有些许喧杂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:33.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是这两天三天却是平静的过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.51,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃 看着吧 今天一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.88,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.05,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}早上好夫人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.01,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}鸡蛋我就收下了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.77,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停停停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.31,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天我绝对不会再放过你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.66,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么样 母鸡混蛋们 已经结束了吗 给我滚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:04.70,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅 我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.74,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.91,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}路上小心 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,155)\fad(300,300)}第2话 春天的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:12.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就是这样了 要说和以前有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.59,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那就是我的工作增加了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.27,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是的 我说小杏 这一点都不好笑好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.52,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.73,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅才刚来 不久就会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.98,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.32,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘛 反正也不像是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.49,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就当助人为乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.50,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽说小祖也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:50.10,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是要环游世界的话果然还是大型摩托比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.96,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.50,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这里是摩托车店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:58.96,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}附近的人都会到这里来买车或者修车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.76,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们小时候就知道这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.09,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}离学校也不远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:09.01,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}更重要的是还有能悠闲休息的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.98,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}放学后不知不觉四个人就逛过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.69,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利绘仔 你真想去环游世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.94,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}YES 还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.86,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骑着摩托车去美国之类的不是很棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.78,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骑着小祖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:27.16,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是啊 果然还是小祖好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.62,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}可以和狼群玩赛跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:32.71,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.92,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然还是要大型的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.29,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不不 我还是相信小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.96,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}所以说不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你太受辛西娅影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.09,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.39,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的 不必隐藏 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.06,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(296,38)}《我在世界的旅行2 三芳律子》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连小夜也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:56.77,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}看吧看吧 春乃前辈也坦率点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.65,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}坦率吗 果然就是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.78,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦？什么什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.91,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想听我昨天作的曲子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.66,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想听想听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.83,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}长篇动化爱犬马洛 敬请各位欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.33,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 马洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.21,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}马洛的节奏掌握的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.13,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.38,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}简直就是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.72,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家有在听曲子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.84,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:32.26,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}总觉得和平时的感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:36.56,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}听了辛西娅的话后就产生灵感了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.85,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小杏也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.06,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.94,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}听她讲话的时候受到启发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:49.37,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不过 以辛西娅的印象来说这曲子有些太古可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.79,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}错错错 看来你不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:55.58,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这里从反面进行表现才是成功的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:16:00.79,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就像那个金吾和银吾就是凭藉以前流行的样子来卖座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大成功什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:07.26,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}所以说呢 曲子完成后就拜托你演唱了 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.30,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}杏里前辈专属歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.36,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}又是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.64,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你自己和马洛一起唱不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.52,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:17.81,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唱歌一定要是春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.02,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是既定事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.98,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}从你在纳凉歌喉自满大会上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:25.44,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}获得史上最年少冠军的那一日起就已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.32,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}上啊 不要输给马洛啊 春乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.99,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目标全美制霸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.24,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}成为世界顶级歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:33.20,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.20,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}多丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.96,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不好意思吵到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:43.17,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}会害羞 就说明春乃前辈其实也想成为那样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.96,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.68,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}以前倒是经常说呢 想要成为歌手之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.56,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}歌喉自满大会是迈向梦想的第一步之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.85,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}都说不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.27,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那是我的黑历史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:04.23,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再说了 在这种山区里唱歌什么的 谁会听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.48,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.82,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}跑了挺长的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.07,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}帮我看看有没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.58,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}保养得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.54,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我每天都会检查一遍的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.29,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.63,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.42,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅小姐也一起来喝杯茶吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.96,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好啊 加上我加上我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.72,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在外面不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}听曲子前先告诉你一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:40.23,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}里面拍了非常可爱的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:40.94,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:44.80,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}估计让你别出声来也不行 所以只给你看3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.11,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}之后注意力要集中在曲子上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.19,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.86,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.28,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}二...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.70,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}三 好结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.29,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}超级好听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.00,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很好 得到了很高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.55,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}得到了通往世界的敲门砖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.01,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是杏里制作的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.93,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.14,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唱歌的是春乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:15.72,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.14,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}完成了要让我听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:19.93,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你们怎么就这么有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.56,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}呐呐 辛西娅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.73,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骑摩托去旅行的话 最先去哪比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.49,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}去你想去的地方就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.45,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.41,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.45,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那种事怎么能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.91,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没关系的 做得到做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.71,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}即使没有确定目的地一下子冲出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.00,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也一定能到达一个很美好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.75,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.76,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}首先要先试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.30,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.93,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不要说这么不负责任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅和我们是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.43,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}比如说出生地 成长环境 思考方式之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.35,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大小之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.06,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:11.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅是出生于澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.94,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}而我们出生在这样的小城镇中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:20.28,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅是普通的摩托车的话 我们只是轻型摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.50,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能做到的事本来就是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:28.13,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}话虽如此 利绘只是说说自己的梦想有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.04,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:36.80,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}而且真的要说的话 春乃前辈肯定也有妄想过实现什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}从没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.27,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我的歌也就最多只能在歌喉自满大会上唱唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:49.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抱歉 我得把早上收到的蔬菜拿回家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.40,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:53.53,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅在摩托车检查完之前一直会在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.90,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.78,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.20,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.07,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.03,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.00,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这辆摩托和越野自行车相比
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.97,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能去到的地方是不一样的吧 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.55,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是取决于骑的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.77,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我是不是很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:33.11,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和骑这辆摩托的小姐发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.99,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}并不是辛西娅的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:41.12,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们的关系不能变得亲近可能是我的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:44.41,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是我太渺小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:51.38,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新东西最初总是不太适应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.75,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这并不需要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.51,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} 慢慢磨合就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:00.47,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是这样...的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:12.02,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家都受辛西娅的影响太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:17.61,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}人类的差别大小就是指这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.78,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.41,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘛...虽然预料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.62,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}味噌碉堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.87,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)\alpha&H33&}味噌碉堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.96,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,500)\alpha&H77&}味噌碉堡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.96,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃 给你看样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}马洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.72,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你去小杏家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.30,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh YES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.06,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天我把我的杯子拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.69,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然是用来吃荞麦面用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:55.23,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.49,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不试试的话就不知道结果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}干嘛 特地为了说这个而来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.17,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}才不是 这是春乃说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:21.42,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小夜啊 杏里啊 利绘啊都说以前春乃经常这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:31.06,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃 去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:36.06,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}去海边去海边 两个人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.98,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了突然间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:38.77,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你要什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.32,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:42.95,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.03,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.70,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不不不 妈妈她们会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.83,Default2,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我以为你们会阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:56.63,Default2,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么能会阻止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:23:00.25,Default2,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}晚上骑车观光也别有一番风味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.46,Default2,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:10.72,Default2,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅 春乃就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:15.10,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好的 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:16.48,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你要这样子去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:17.23,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.98,Default2,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}以前我用过的那个 状态很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:24.44,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这样就可以和你一起跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:28.24,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们出发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.16,Default2,Parents,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:41.59,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}太暗了 前面都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:49.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是没有想像中的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是因为和辛西娅在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.62,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然很难追上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.62,0:24:12.45,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也完全提不起速度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:17.25,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就这样 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:23.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明明这么慢却感觉 这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:30.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再稍微 加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:35.72,Default2,Mechanic,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这取决于骑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:38.85,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}以前春乃经常这样说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.90,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的要出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:43.82,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:45.69,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}都是大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.69,0:24:46.90,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.86,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不试试的话怎么知道不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:51.99,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为不试试的话怎么知道不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.00,0:25:00.37,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能到哪儿都取决于我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.83,0:25:03.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:08.59,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}所以反正是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:14.01,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我觉得一个人能做到的事是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:19.02,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}到底开了多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.98,0:25:23.31,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}都过了好几个山口了却还是看不见海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.31,0:25:28.99,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}差不多到极限了 过了那个山口就到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.37,0:25:39.50,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:47.34,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:55.47,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的是海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:25:58.85,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:01.02,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:04.23,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}为什么我会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.94,0:26:07.48,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.82,0:26:13.74,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.74,0:26:16.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.24,0:26:21.54,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我没想到真的能来到海边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:23.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}多亏了辛西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.21,0:26:24.46,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:26.50,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我帮到春乃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.50,0:26:29.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 帮到我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:32.34,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}太好了 太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:38.51,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我再一次发觉了 一个人的话什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.51,0:26:40.81,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:48.11,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}像辛西娅这样凭自己什么都能做到的人 真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.65,0:26:52.28,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我并不是一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.24,0:26:58.87,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也是 而且谁都是一样的 并不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.12,0:27:03.46,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也借助了这些孩子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.46,0:27:08.25,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不仅如此 制造摩托车的人 造路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:12.96,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很多很多的人将我们带到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.34,0:27:20.72,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}旅行的途中 我就一直这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.72,0:27:25.94,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很多素未蒙面的人帮助着我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.69,0:27:32.48,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}所以我无论去哪里都能到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:41.49,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我觉得啊 春乃也是去不断试试借助谁的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.99,0:27:49.36,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.66,0:27:51.88,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.88,0:27:54.03,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}骗人 都湿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.63,0:27:57.26,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没事 马上就会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.01,0:28:01.81,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不断借助他人的力量就好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:06.94,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是我从没想过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.85,0:28:10.36,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}人并不是独自一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.36,0:28:13.48,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这像是电视剧常见的台词般的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.48,0:28:16.74,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可思议间滑落心中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.40,0:28:32.24,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,深く息を吸い込んでみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.34,0:28:43.03,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,肩の力をそっと抜いて ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.03,0:28:48.85,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,大きな声で歌ってみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.95,0:28:58.87,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かにこの歌が届くかな
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.89,0:29:05.70,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,吹き抜ける 風の中ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.60,0:29:16.70,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,言えずに隠してた 不安もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.62,0:29:26.55,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,手を伸ばそう どこまでも続いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:33.71,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,まぶしい光を つかまえたら
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.81,0:29:43.17,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,歩き出そう この場所から始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.27,0:29:54.56,kanji2,,0000,0000,0000,,どこかで誰かが キミの事を待っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.40,0:28:32.24,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,试着深呼吸看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.34,0:28:43.03,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀也放松 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.03,0:28:48.85,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,试着大声地歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.95,0:28:58.87,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,或许能传达给谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.89,0:29:05.70,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,在风中独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.60,0:29:16.70,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏不能言语的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.62,0:29:26.55,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,伸出双手 如果能将那
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:33.71,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,一直延续的光芒抓住的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.81,0:29:43.17,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 就从这里开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.27,0:29:54.56,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一定有人在那里等着你